fields.name: Burton Elite Full-Zip Hoodie Black
fields.more_info:
Regular fit is just right: Not too tight or too baggy

89% organic cotton, 11% recycled polyester 306gsm brushed-back fleece

Jersey-lined hood with drawcord

Ribbed cuffs and hem

Patch-on hand-warmer pockets

Screen-printed logos
fields.text:
Zip into this classic hoodie and get out the door with time to spare.

The Burton Elite Full-Zip Hoodie is the simple jacket solution you're looking for, because there's no reason to perform calculus when elementary math will do the trick. A drawcord hood provides coverage to keep cold air away from your neck and head, and patch-on hand-warmer pockets shield your hands from windy weather.

fields.name: Burton Longsleeve shirt Green
fields.more_info:
Straight from the Forager deck to your back with Family Tree-inspired graphics to keep you dreaming of more ride time.

Following the clean aesthetic of the board graphics, the men's Burton Forager Long Sleeve T-Shirt channels the playful but precise feel of the board designed in collaboration with legendary rider Masa Takeuchi. Soft organic cotton means it feels great from first wear.
fields.text:
